item.title: CVE-2020-3215|2024-09-17T00:55:29.501Z -- cisco -- cisco%20ios%20xe%20software%203.8.0s
item.description: A vulnerability in the Virtual Services Container of Cisco IOS XE Software could allow an authenticated, local attacker to gain root-level privileges on an affected device. The vulnerability is due to insufficient validation of a user-supplied open virtual appliance (OVA). An attacker could exploit this vulnerability by installing a malicious OVA on an affected device.
